<s> Furukawa Co. of Japan said it will acquire two construction machinery plants and a sales unit in France formerly belonging to Dresser Industries Inc. of the U.S. . </s>
<s> The company said it made the purchase in order to locally produce hydraulically operated shovels . </s>
<s> Last October , the company also bought a wheel-loader manufacturing plant in Heidelberg , West Germany , from Dresser . </s>
<s> Furukawa said the purchase of the French and German plants together will total about 40 billion yen -LRB- $ 280 million -RRB- . </s>
